{{vgname|刺客信条|en=Assassin's Creed|tw=刺客教條}}是由[[育碧公司|育碧公司]]的[[育碧蒙特利尔|蒙特利爾]]工作室開發的一款[[第三人称視角|第三人称視角遊戲]][[動作冒險|動作冒險遊戲]][[潜行|隱蔽類遊戲]]類遊戲，本系列始於2007年11月在[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]上發行。[[Windows|Windows]]版追加了內容並更名為《刺客教條：導演剪輯版》（''Assassin's Creed: Director's Cut Edition''），於2008年4月推出。

== 遊戲系統 ==
界面採用開放世界第三人稱視角，以主角追溯其刺客祖先記憶而控制其行動。遊戲引入「社會狀態圖像」（Social Status Icon）從而讓主角能了解附近敵兵與區域對其祖先的注意程度及警戒狀態{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': The Social Status Icon [Exposed, Cool Down, Vanishing, Vanished, Anonymous] gives you information on your social status.}}，並以「高姿態」（High Profile）及「低姿態」（Low Profile）區分行動性質{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': The Animus differentiates between two fundamental actions: Low Profile and High Profile.}}：低姿態行為較容易被社會接受{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': Low Profile actions are socially acceptable.}}；高姿態行為以行動為中心{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': High Profile actions are more action-oriented.}}（例如擒拿和拋擲敵人、疾跑）。一旦附近區域對其祖先出現高度警戒狀態，其祖先可選擇把應戰敵兵殺死或逃離敵兵視線範圍並躲藏直至警戒回復正常。

其祖先之生命值以主角及祖先之間之「同步值」（Sychronization）顯示{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': The Sychronization Bar measures your sychronization with your ancestor.}}：作出與真實記憶不合之事（如受傷或傷及無辜）會使同步值下降，失去之同步值能透過重新經歷祖先之生活而遂漸回復{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': Should you lose sych, you can restore sychronization by reliving key moments of your ancestor's life, or by respecting the Creed.}}，降至零點會導致記憶重新開始{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': If you ever fall completely out of sych, the Animus will retore you to your last sychronized position.}}；作出與真實記憶相同之事（如拯救市民或在每次刺殺行動前對目標作出全面調查）會使同步最高值逐漸提升。完全同步時主角可使用其祖先之第六感官「鷹眼視界」（Eagle Vision）以感知附近人們對其祖先之態度{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': Now that you are fully syched, a new ability is available to you. Refered to as Eagle Vision, this sixth sense helped your ancestor understand the intentions of the people around him.}}{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': Remember, Eagle Vision will only be available when you are fully syched.}}。

== 故事劇情 ==
2012年9月1日04:02<ref>《[[刺客教條IV：黑旗|刺客教條IV：黑旗]]》，Abstergo Entertainment 地图二楼右侧二级安全房间的左下的电脑「戴斯蒙文件包」。</ref>，酒保[[戴斯蒙德·迈尔斯|戴斯蒙·迈尔斯]]被跨國製藥公司Abstergo 劫持作為基因記憶追溯機器「Animus」{{efn|'''Vidic''': You're inside the Animus. '''Desmond''': Which is...? '''Vidic''': It's a projector that renders genetic memories into three dimensions.}}的第十七個實驗體{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': Hello, Subject Seventeen.}}，目的為獲得其活躍於1191年[[第三次十字軍東征|第三次十字軍東征]]時期、隸屬[[敍利亞|敍利亞]][[阿薩辛派|刺客組織]]之刺客祖先－[[阿泰爾·伊本·拉阿哈德|阿泰爾·伊本·拉阿哈德]]（Altaïr ibn La-Ahad）的一段記憶。

當年阿泰爾奉命與兩名同伴到[[所羅門聖殿|所羅門聖殿]]尋找一個古代遺物，卻對於自己過度自信{{efn|'''Altaïr''': Robert de Sablé. His life is mine. '''Malik''': No! We were asked to retrieve the treasure and deal with Robert only if necessasry. '''Altaïr''': He stands between us and it. I'd say it's necessary. '''Malik''': Discretion, Altaïr!. '''Altaïr''': You mean cowardice. That man is our greatest enemy, and here we have a chance to be rid of him. '''Malik''': You have already broken two tenets of our creed. Now you would break the third: do not compromise the brotherhood. '''Altaïr''': I am your superior, in both title and ability. Youl should know better than to question me.}}，不但被刺客之宿敵[[聖殿騎士團|聖殿騎士團]]阻止{{efn|'''Robert''': I spare you only that you may return to your master and deliver a message.}}且違背了三大刺客教條{{efn|'''Rashid''': Three simple tenets, which you seem to forget. I will remind you.}}：不殺無辜{{efn|'''Rashid''': First and foremost: Stay your blade... '''Altaïr''': from the flesh of an innocent. I know.}}、不暴露行蹤{{efn|'''Rashid''': The second tenet is that which gives us strength. Hide in plain sight. Let the people mask you such that you become one with the crowd.}}、不連累刺客組織{{efn|'''Rashid''': The third and final tenet, the worst of all your betrayals. Never compromise the brotherhood.}}{{efn|'''In-game Animus tutorial program''': The Creed consists of three tenets. First, never hurt an innocent person. Second, always be discreet. Third, do not compromise the clan.}}<ref>Memory Block 1</ref>。於回到刺客組織位於[[馬西亞夫|馬西亞夫]]的堡壘後，刺客組織之首[[拉希德丁·锡南|拉希德丁·锡南]]（Rashid ad-Din Sinan）把阿泰爾降至最低級別{{efn|'''Rashid''': You'll see that you've been stripped of all your possessions. Your rank as well. You are a novice, a child once more, as you were on the day you first joined our Order.}}，同時命其刺殺九名位於聖地（[[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]、[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]、[[阿卡_(以色列)|阿卡]]）內的騎士團重要人物以作贖罪{{efn|'''Rashid''': I am offering you a chance at redemption. You'll earn your way back into the brotherhood.}}，為[[十字軍|十字軍]]及[[撒拉森|撒拉森]]勢力之間帶來和平{{efn|'''Rashid''': I hold here a list. Nine names adorn it. Nine men who need to die. They are plague bringers, war makers. Their power and influence corrupts the land and ensures the Crusades continue. You will find them. Kill them. In doing so, you sow the seeds of peace, both for the region, and for yourself. In this way you might be redeemed.}}。

阿泰爾把各人逐一刺殺，並了解眾人之目的為利用從所羅門聖殿取得之古代遺物控制人民思想以帶來和平，而聖殿騎士團之最終計劃為聯合十字軍及撒拉森勢力以摧毀刺客組織<ref>Memory Blocks 2, 3, 4, 5</ref>，但阿泰爾在刺殺最後一名目標－聖殿騎士團大團長[[薩布萊的羅伯特四世|羅貝爾·德·薩布萊]]後始悉拉希德丁乃聖殿騎士{{efn|'''Robert''': Nine men he sent you to kill, yes? The nine who guarded the treasure's secret. '''Altaïr''': What of it? '''Robert''': It wasn't nine who found the treasure, Assassin. Not nine, but ten. '''Altaïr''': A tenth? None may live to carry the secret. Give me his name. '''Robert''': Oh, but you know him well, and I doubt very much you'd take his life, as willingly as you've taken mine. '''Altaïr''': Who? '''Robert''': It is your master, Al Mualim.}}，因企圖獨佔遺物而派遣阿泰爾刺殺其餘九人{{efn|'''Altaïr''': I have no interest in the treasure. '''Robert''': Ah, but he does. The only difference between your master and I, is that he did not want to share.}}<ref>Memory Block 6</ref>：該遺物名為「[[伊甸|伊甸]]碎片」{{efn|'''Rashid''': That's all it's ever done, this Templar treasure, this... Piece of Eden.}}，能控制人類思想及造出幻象{{efn|'''Rashid''': He who holds it commands the hearts and minds of whoever looks upon it, whoever tastes of it, as they say.}}，而古代之超自然現像包括[[古埃及|古埃及]]法師把手杖變成蛇、[[摩西|摩西]]分[[紅海|紅海]]、[[特洛伊戰爭|特洛伊戰爭]]中神明顯靈、[[迦拿的婚禮|迦拿的婚禮]]中水變成酒等全為此遺物造出之幻象{{efn|'''Rashid''': This... piece of silver, cast out Adam and Eve. It turned staves into snakes, parted and closed the Red Sea. Eris used it to start the Trojin War, and with it, a poor carpenter turned water into wine.}}{{efn|'''Rashid''': Do you understand now? The Rea Sea was never parted. Water never turned to wine. It was not the machinations of Eris that spawned the Trojan War, but this! Illusions! All of them!}}。在阿泰爾回到刺客組織堡壘後{{efn|'''Rashid''': So... the student returns. '''Altaïr''': I've never been one to run. '''Rashid''': Never been one to listen either.}}，拉希德丁利用碎片造出各種幻象與阿泰爾展開決鬥。阿泰爾擊破各幻術後刺殺拉希德丁{{efn|'''Rashid''': Impossible. The student does not defeat the teacher. '''Altaïr''': La'a shay'a waqi'un moutlaq bale kouloun moumkine. '''Rashid''': So it seems. You have won then. Go, and claim your prize.}}，碎片亦於此時投射出全世界其餘多塊碎片位置的立體影像<ref>Memory Block 7</ref>。

Abstergo 在取得該段記憶後{{efn|'''Abstergo''': Well? '''Vidic''': We've got the map.}}計劃把戴斯蒙留待日後處決{{efn|'''Lucy''': We might need him, his memories. I'd recommend we hold him until we have confirmation that there aren't any surprises waiting for us at the sites. '''Abstergo''': Very well. Ensure we have no further need of him, then kill him.}}，但戴斯蒙在研究人員離開後{{efn|'''Vidic''': Don't get too comfortable, Mr. Miles! We'll be back for you soon enough.}}看見實驗室地上及牆上出現以鮮血寫成之文字：因長期進入Animus 而出現之副作用－「出血效應」（Bleeding Effect）使戴斯蒙擁有了鷹眼視覺{{efn|'''Assassin's Creed II'''. '''Lucy''': We're going to train you - turn you into one of us. '''Desmond''': What?! No, no... you've seen me in action - I'm no good at this. And even if I was... it would take months - years, even. '''Lucy''': No. Not with the Animus. Not with the bleeding effect... If you can follow in his footsteps, you'll learn everything he did - just like he did. Years of training absorbed in a matter of days.}}，看見第十六實驗體自殺前以血寫下之[[2012年預言|2012年預言]]及其他加密訊息{{efn|'''Desmond''': Oh my god! It looks like... is that blood? Who the hell were they keeping here before me? What happened to him? What does it mean, I wonder.}}。

