遊戲普遍獲得正面評價。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]表示遊玩過程沒有進步，最終變得沈悶而且過於重複<ref>[http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=87432&page=3 Assassin's Creed Review // Xbox 360 /// Eurogamer]</ref>。Electronic Gaming Monthly成員Andrew P.於評論中認為遊戲的[[跑酷|跑酷]]式逃生路線富挑戰性<ref>Andrew P., "Review of ''Assassin's Creed''," ''Electronic Gaming Monthly'' 224 (January 2008): 89.</ref>。[[Fami通|Fami通]]以40分為滿分下分別為遊戲之Xbox 360版和PS3版給予36分和37分，讚揚了遊戲劇情、表達手法和主角之高難度動作，但對過於簡單之戰鬥系統、地圖和視角問題作出批評<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.n4g.com/News-86589.aspx |title=Famitsu reviews Dragon Quest IV, Assassins Creed, Guilty Gear 2 and more |accessdate=2014-09-18 |archive-date=2009-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416143039/http://www.n4g.com/News-86589.aspx |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/11/02/assassins-creed-nabs-37-40-from-famitsu/ |title=Assassin's Creed nabs 37/40 from Famitsu |access-date=2014-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009090600/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/11/02/assassins-creed-nabs-37-40-from-famitsu/ |archive-date=2014-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]以10分為滿分下給予遊戲9.5分，讚揚遊戲之操作系統、重玩價值和吸引的劇情，但認為情報打聽的任務過於重複<ref>''Game Informer'', December 2007 issue</ref>。ESPN成員Aaron Boulding認為遊戲之社會潛行概念相當創新，而且設計者在視覺上捕捉了神髓。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/videogames/news/story?id=3129115 |title=ESPN – Easy Points – 'Tis the Season – Videogames |accessdate=2014-09-18 |archive-date=2007-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071201120017/http://sports.espn.go.com/videogames/news/story?id=3129115 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]同樣表揚了遊戲的劇情並對此給予9.7分，但指出重複度高的玩法與下等的人工智能使遊戲的潛質下降，認為遊戲雖有所突破但未能做好部分基本要素<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gametrailers.com/player/27754.html |title=GameTrailers ''Assassin's Creed'' Video Review |accessdate=2014-09-18 |archive-date=2009-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090504202631/http://www.gametrailers.com/player/27754.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]為遊戲給予10分滿分；[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]為遊戲之Xbox 360與PS3版各給予81分<ref name="mcps3" /><ref name="mcx360" />。[[GamePro|GamePro]]認為如果玩家願意付出耐性，遊戲能提供部分最佳的遊玩體驗<ref name="GamePro">{{cite web|url=http://gamepro.com/microsoft/xbox360/games/reviews/146348.shtml|title=''Assassin's Creed'' review|author=Melick, Todd|date=November 14, 2007|publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]]|accessdate=2008-01-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071110130850/http://www.gamepro.com/microsoft/xbox360/games/reviews/146348.shtml|archivedate=2007-11-10|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。Hyper雜誌成員Darren Wells讚揚遊戲劇情、畫面和操作，但批評部分任務不大適合電腦平台而且選單系統設計不佳<ref>{{cite journal|last=Wells|first=Darren|date=June 2008|title=Assassin's Creed|journal=[[Hyper_(magazine)|Hyper]]|publisher=[[Next_Media|Next Media]]|issue=176|page=54|issn=1320-7458}}</ref>。

